summary: An email from an FBI Special Agent in the New York Field Office transmitting a federal trial subpoena related to the Epstein case. The email originates from the Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk.

persons.name: Special Agent
persons.context: Sends an email from the FBI New York Field Office, Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk, transmitting a federal trial subpoena.

events.title: Trial Subpoena Issuance
events.description: An FBI Special Agent transmits a federal trial subpoena via email.

keyFacts: A federal trial subpoena was issued on November 15, 2021, in relation to the Epstein case.
The subpoena was transmitted by an FBI Special Agent from the New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk.
The document reference EFTA00155594 is associated with this correspondence.
